modName: Savegame Resource - Get a Head Start
summary:
Savegame resource with Nord following Imperial path - intensive care has been into developing this savegame so that it gives a good head-start into the game.
Is made with and requires version 1.9.32.0 of Skyrim.
Vanilla and Legendary Edition savegames available
No ENB(s), no additional scripts, no codes used, no SKSE, no ScriptDr
descriptionHtml:
*Version 3 requires all official DLC (Cleaned with TES5edit) and the Unofficial Patches.*

Character name: Slade Murdok
Race: Nord
Gender: Male
Level: 1 (Can level up to level 8)
Path taken at Helgen: Imperial
Equipment state: Decent equipment and gold for his level. Some enchanted items.
Equipment Locations: In Lydia's inventory and character's own inventory.
Quests started: 7 including main quests up to the Horn of Jurgen Windcaller
Quests finished: 4 of the first main quests.
Standing Stone chosen: Warrior or Steed(Version 3)
Main skills: Archery, Sneak, One-handed, Two-handed, and Light Armour.
Skill books collected and read: 5-10
Locations Discovered: 35+
Criminal Record: None
Titles: Thane of Whiterun, Dragonborn

Please contact me if you find any problems.
author: PlanetSlayer
